OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1781470068
OL,3,CPerforming arts school to close
OL,4,Cdespite parent protests
OL,6,FParents have lost their High Court
OL,7,Ffight to prevent the closure of a
OL,8,Fperforming arts school - despite their
OL,9,Fcampaign to keep it open.
OL,11,FThe LIPA primary school and secondary
OL,12,Fschool, run by an academy trust
OL,13,Fspecialising in performing arts,
OL,14,Fannounced in February it would close
OL,15,Fat the end of the academic year.
OL,17,FThe school, which opened in 2014, is
OL,18,Ffor children aged 4-16 and is not
OL,19,Fconnected to the Liverpool Institute
OL,20,Ffor Performing Arts (LIPA) that was
OL,21,Ffounded by Sir Paul McCartney.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
