PN,36802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1781470068
OL,3,CPerforming arts school to close
OL,4,Cdespite parent protests
OL,6,FBased in Liverpool city centre, the
OL,7,Fschool has faced a financial deficit
OL,8,Fand falling pupil numbers, and was
OL,9,Frated inadequate in its latest OFSTED
OL,10,Freport.
OL,12,FBut teachers and parents say many
OL,13,Fimprovements have been made since.
OL,15,FAfter the announcement concerned
OL,16,Fparents and supporters filed a legal
OL,17,Freview in the High Court to stop the
OL,18,Fplanned closure of the Upper
OL,19,FParliament School.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1781470068
OL,3,CPerforming arts school to close
OL,4,Cdespite parent protests
OL,6,FBut, on 11 June, a judge dismissed
OL,7,Ftheir claim, and the school will close
OL,8,Fin July.
OL,10,FMany parents had moved their children
OL,11,Fto others schools when the news broke
OL,12,Fit could close - but told ITV News
OL,13,Fthey would move them back if it was to
OL,14,Fremain open.
OL,16,FTeachers have been trying to keep
OL,17,Fclasses running to ensure pupils who
OL,18,Fhave stayed in the school are catered
OL,19,Ffor.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1781470068
OL,3,CPerforming arts school to close
OL,4,Cdespite parent protests
OL,6,FOne student, Year 10 pupil Alice
OL,7,FMather-Mulholland, chose to stay
OL,8,Fdespite many of her friends having
OL,9,Falready left.
OL,11,F"The teachers are still trying,
OL,12,Fthey're trying to make it as normal as
OL,13,Fit can be no matter how many people
OL,14,Fhave left, whether there's five people
OL,15,Fleft in your class or 15," she said
OL,16,Fbefore the decision was made.
OL,18,F"You can still see that everyone is
OL,19,Ftrying really, really hard to keep it
OL,20,Fopen."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1781470068
OL,3,CPerforming arts school to close
OL,4,Cdespite parent protests
OL,6,FDouglas Trafford - another Year 10
OL,7,Fstudent who chose to stay at LIPA
OL,8,FSchool until a final decision is made
OL,9,F- said: "You've got to carry on,
OL,10,Fyou've got to pretend nothing else has
OL,11,Fhappened.
OL,13,F"The classes are small, but the
OL,14,Fteachers are highly focused on what we
OL,15,Fneed."
OL,17,FMichelle Mooney - who moved her
OL,18,Fdaughter to another school when the
OL,19,Fpotential closure was announced - has
OL,20,Fnow moved her back to LIPA School.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1781470068
OL,3,CPerforming arts school to close
OL,4,Cdespite parent protests
OL,6,FShe said: "When she got moved into the
OL,7,Fother school, there was no film
OL,8,Fstudies, no performing arts.
OL,10,F"This is a performing arts school, and
OL,11,Fthere's no other performing arts
OL,12,Fschools available to her."
OL,14,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,15,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,16,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,17,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
